                  "text": "Create a server, add friends, or start a conversation.",
                  "color": "#b9bbbe",
                  "fontSize": "16px"
                },
                "instructions": {
                  "color": "#b9bbbe",
                  "fontSize": "14px",
                  "marginTop": "20px",
                  "items": [
                    "Click the ‚öô menu button (bottom left) to create a server or access features",
